;;
;;   m a |rss:http://lwn.net/http://lwn.net/headlines/newrss|+lwn
;;
;; An Atom, RSS or OPML feed can be used for an access group:
;;
;;    m A rss:http://planet.gnome.org/atom.xml
;;
;;
